name: Chewbacca (V)
Lore: 'Wookiee smuggler from Kashyyyk. Over 200 years old. Top-notch mechanic and pilot. Jabba has large bounty on this ''walking carpet''. Friends call him Chewie...or Fuzzball.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots.  During your turn, may use 1 Force to take one Chewie''s AT-ST, Chewbacca''s Bowcaster, That''s One, or an Interrupt with ''Chewie'' or ''Wookiee'' in game text into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.(Errata Text - September 9th, 2009)',
